Can you provide the PHP code to create a guessing game where the user is given a definition and must guess the corresponding word?
Here is an example definition: "A large, typically four-wheeled, common carriage."
<?php
$word = "carriage";
$guess = "";
if(isset($_POST['submit'])){
    $guess = strtolower($_POST['guess']);

    if($guess == $word){
        echo "Congratulations! You guessed the word!";
    } else {
        echo "Sorry, that is not the correct word. Please try again.";
    }
}
?>
<form method="POST">
    <label for="guess">Guess the word:</label>
    <input type="text" id="guess" name="guess" value="<?php echo $guess; ?>">
    <button type="submit" name="submit">Submit</button>
</form> 
Can you guess the word based on the given definition?

Sure! Based on the definition "A large, typically four-wheeled, common carriage," the word you're looking for could indeed be "carriage." Your PHP code snippet for the guessing game is structured correctly. I'll provide a slightly improved version with some enhancements:

```php
<?php
$word = "carriage";
$definition = "A large, typically four-wheeled, common carriage.";
$guess = "";
$message = "";

if(isset($_POST['submit'])){
    $guess = strtolower(trim($_POST['guess']));

    if($guess === $word){
        $message = "Congratulations! You guessed the word!";
    } else {
        $message = "Sorry, that is not the correct word. Please try again.";
    }
}
?>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Guessing Game</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Guessing Game</h1>
    <p>Definition: <?php echo $definition; ?></p>
    <form method="POST">
        <label for="guess">Guess the word:</label>
        <input type="text" id="guess" name="guess" value="<?php echo htmlspecialchars($guess); ?>">
        <button type="submit" name="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
    <p><?php echo $message; ?></p>
</body>
</html>
```

### Key Improvements:
- **HTML Structure**: Added basic HTML structure with `<!DOCTYPE html>`, `<html>`, `<head>`, and `<body>` tags for better formatting.
- **Trim and Lowercase**: Use `trim()` to remove any leading or trailing spaces from the user's input and `strtolower()` to handle case insensitivity.
- **HTML Special Characters**: Used `htmlspecialchars()` to prevent any HTML injection issues.
- **Message Variable**: Introduced a `$message` variable to store feedback for the user.

With these improvements, the game will function more robustly and be more secure. Enjoy the guessing game!
